FBIS3-54989 "drsov003_r_94013" FBIS-SOV-94-003 Document Type:Daily Report 5 Jan 1994 Azerbaijan State Committee for Reforms Established NC0401220594 Baku Radio Baku Network in Azeri 0400 GMT 30 Dec 93 NC0401220594 Baku Radio Baku Network Language: Azeri Article Type:BFN [Text] The State Committee for Reforms has been established to effect economic reforms in Azerbaijan. It will draw up concrete reform programs and outline the mechanisms required to realize them. Ruhshen Mustafayev, director of the Institute of State Construction and Internaional Relations, has been appointed to head the new committee.
